      "text": "うんうん、ミクちゃんの衣装ってみんな可愛いよね\nそれに一瞬で着替えちゃうなんて本当に凄いよ……！",
      "startTime": 17.7666665197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
